Detecting Opinion Spam in Hotel Reviews by training on a known set of Genuine and Fake Reviews.
Uses the following:
- scikit-learn for training a Machine Learning model using Logistic Regression
- nltk for POS tagging

The following features are being used:
- Number of sentiment carrying words in the review
- The number of verbs in the review
- The number of nouns in a review
- The length of the review
